  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tilemancer dungeon is a minimalist dungeon crawler - card game where you create & explore your own dungeon by placing down room tiles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your own path</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/6c312b5afae0389f49a8d4562811e1ed.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/6c312b5afae0389f49a8d4562811e1ed.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/6c312b5afae0389f49a8d4562811e1ed.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place tiles in the dungeon, in a card-like manner, to create your own path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tile is a room that must be placed in a sequence so it connects to a previously placed tile. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each room contains either :</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An enemy<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/449d9724dfc715bc99388df06256ac45.webp?t=1764508421\" width=168 height=32 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lootable chest<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/eea0f74f08933d9b3723d0bcdf6333bc.webp?t=1764508421\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A weapon<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/b5c0a524ddce14ebf59c1b9c90925be6.webp?t=1764508421\" width=128 height=32 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A consumable<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/658a2e75c1d387c9cc8429ec28e23343.webp?t=1764508421\" width=128 height=32 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A trap<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/9be6832ebb675d9270b43e21c08600d1.webp?t=1764508421\" width=64 height=32 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A piece of equipment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/df51a9f656ad5ad23f41aa05e45d5c17.webp?t=1764508421\" width=128 height=32 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight your way through the dungeon</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3ab8d59262a8ca1933a99321dc722cf9.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3ab8d59262a8ca1933a99321dc722cf9.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3ab8d59262a8ca1933a99321dc722cf9.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your weapons & abilities to make your way through the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set a target for your hero and he will move and fight on his own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternate cleverly between enemies, potions & equipmentto survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather new playable allies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat other heroes to free them from the influence of the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They will join your team as a new playable hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero has his own abilities & his own way to navigate through the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Knight</strong>s</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/996ae215e2c438e2875a602ef21639b4.apng?t=1764508421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/996ae215e2c438e2875a602ef21639b4.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=108 height=52 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave and strong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with their mighty sword and their sturdy shield, they will face their enemies head on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Berserker</strong>s</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/50b1eceb6136e3e0f29972ca469bb887.apng?t=1764508421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/50b1eceb6136e3e0f29972ca469bb887.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=108 height=52 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A big axe and a bad temper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They build up rage that makes them hit harder the more they fight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Wizard & The Witch</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/1b2baa5a1bdfb1cc17505a2ada4e0117.apng?t=1764508421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/1b2baa5a1bdfb1cc17505a2ada4e0117.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=108 height=52 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old and wise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They can draw in their mana to cast powerful fireballs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Rogue</strong>s</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/9dc53db79095cff63766df3a11eb5fa8.apng?t=1764508421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/9dc53db79095cff63766df3a11eb5fa8.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=108 height=52 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneaky and light-footed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They can avoid traps, sneak on enemies and lure them into traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Cultists</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/9aaa6fefd810f76d0ee13ce835210665.apng?t=1764508421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/9aaa6fefd810f76d0ee13ce835210665.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=108 height=52 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Versed in the dark and the occult.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They draw their power from their enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gear up</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather equipment in the dungeon or spend your hard earned coins to upgrade your damages & health. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Claim the dungeon and become the next Tilemancer !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
