eamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/32c033a5fd2610b4d70936611a65d020.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather equipment in the dungeon or spend your hard earned coins to upgrade your damages & health. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Claim the dungeon and become the next Tilemancer !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.poster.avif?t=1764508421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.webm?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998990/extras/3106d868372ec337f5daa657ce057539.mp4?t=1764508421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
